    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and maintained, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs super smoothly and is all set for its next big adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This driver-focused example utilizes the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS service to ensure optimal cam timing. The chassis maintains its composure with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected of the platform. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved performance vehicle, the drivetrain remains tight and the 8,000 RPM redline is as exhilarating as ever. A turn-key opportunity for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
