      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior is finished in a deep Midnight Blue Metallic that still holds a brilliant luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scratch near the rear passenger wheel well, the body remains straight and free of any major dings. Inside, the Oyster-colored perforated leather interior has been smoke-free and professionally detailed. The driver\u2019s seat shows very light bolster wear consistent with regular use, but the rear seats and carpets appear nearly untouched. All technological features\u2014including the panoramic sunroof, premium surround-sound system, and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound. It has a complete service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The tires were replaced last season and currently show approximately 75% tread life remaining, and the brake pads were serviced just three months ago. This car drives smooth, shifts effortlessly, and is ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
